# DEPRECATED — moved from agent/benchmark.py 2026-04-10
# Decision: deprecate for development phase to reduce failure modes.
# This is an optimization/benchmarking tool appropriate for Phase 3+
# after the pipeline produces its first verified output on a real VistA routine.
#
# To reactivate:
#   1. Move back to agent/benchmark.py
#   2. Create tickets/open/BENCH-T01.yaml with clear scope:
#      - What does it benchmark? (routine throughput, token cost, parse time)
#      - What is the pass/fail threshold?
#      - Which phase gates trigger it?
#   3. Add 'agent/benchmark.py' to ALLOWED_TOOLS in scripts/run_tool.py
#   4. Add 'benchmark' to settings.yaml allowed_tools
#   5. Remove this warning header
#
# Original benchmark.py content was present in agent/benchmark.py before this deprecation.
# See git log for the original implementation.
